1
00:00:07,719 --> 00:00:08,359
Captain Wang.

2
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:12,000
I'd like to see anyone try.

3
00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:13,919
As long as I, Jiang Han, am here today,

4
00:00:14,119 --> 00:00:15,919
none of you will lay a finger on my boss.

5
00:00:16,039 --> 00:00:16,640
Jiang Han.

6
00:00:17,760 --> 00:00:18,320
Boss.

7
00:00:18,640 --> 00:00:19,239
With me here today,

8
00:00:19,239 --> 00:00:19,960
they can't take you away.

9
00:00:20,359 --> 00:00:20,920
How dare you!

10
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:06,799
Jiang Han, move aside.

11
00:01:07,159 --> 00:01:08,439
Chief Xing, my boss, he...

12
00:01:08,439 --> 00:01:09,560
You're not even listening to me anymore?

13
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:15,079
Li Kaiyang.

14
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:16,920
Return to the station with them calmly.

15
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,280
And explain everything clearly.

16
00:01:18,959 --> 00:01:19,840
I promise you,

17
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,400
I will find Xing Mingliang.

18
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:22,920
I'll keep Ruolan safe.

19
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:24,719
Alright.

20
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,359
That's all I needed to hear.

21
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,120
Fang Ping.

22
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:29,599
Chief Xing.

23
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:30,480
Skip the formalities.

24
00:01:43,319 --> 00:01:44,280
Get a locksmith here, now.

25
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:44,920
Yes, sir.

26
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:46,840
Lin Xue.

27
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:48,640
Pull the security footage from management.

28
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:44,560
Captain Wang.

29
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,000
Captain Wang.

30
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:47,319
Captain Wang.

31
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:49,360
Xing Mingliang is seen with a large case,

32
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,919
driving off in a black sedan.

33
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:53,560
Wang Yonglin.

34
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,680
Send units to rescue Zhao Ruolan at once.

35
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,080
And interrogate Li Kaiyang.

36
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,360
Yes, Chief Xing.

37
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,479
Boss.

38
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:18,840
Our honored guest has arrived.

39
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:55,879
Boss, this...

40
00:03:58,719 --> 00:03:59,439
Let me ask you.

41
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,439
Why push things this far?

42
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,759
What exactly happened?

43
00:04:03,759 --> 00:04:04,800
My dear Chief Xing.

44
00:04:05,719 --> 00:04:06,599
The way you're talking,

45
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:08,039
you're scaring me.

46
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:09,919
Killing Su Zhuang,

47
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,360
framing Li Kaiyang,

48
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:13,000
did you send someone to do it?

49
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:17,720
Chief Xing, since you're in my room,

50
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,879
watch how you speak.

51
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:20,079
I treat you as a guest,

52
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,480
to catch up and bond.

53
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,560
I treat you as a friend.

54
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:25,279
If you're going to make wild claims

55
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:26,160
and make things up,

56
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,519
I don't have time to humor you.

57
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,319
Believe me, one phone call from me

58
00:04:30,079 --> 00:04:32,240
can turn this place upside down.

59
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,519
Believe me, one phone call from me

60
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:36,160
can cost you the captain's position.

61
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,160
Don't say I didn't warn you.

62
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:47,079
Li Kaiyang

63
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:50,279
isn't someone you can easily take down.

64
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:53,240
Once he's set his mind on something,

65
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,519
he will never give up.

66
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,399
No matter how strong the opponent,

67
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:01,399
he'll charge in without hesitation.

68
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,639
Until he reaches his goal,

69
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,959
he won't stop.

70
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:07,560
Whether he gives up or not,

71
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,319
what's that got to do with me?

72
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:12,959
I'm a law-abiding citizen.

73
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:20,360
Chief Xing,

74
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,720
why make things so difficult?

75
00:05:24,319 --> 00:05:25,240
In your eyes,

76
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:27,519
I probably mean nothing to you.

77
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:28,519
But you,

78
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:30,720
you should think about your son.

79
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,120
He's nothing but an animal.

80
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,920
But he's your own flesh and blood.

81
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:38,360
Don't think that controlling my son

82
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:40,519
means you can use me as a pawn.

83
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:43,920
You are truly wronging me.

84
00:05:44,319 --> 00:05:45,040
It's just that

85
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,920
your son's tastes are rather peculiar.

86
00:05:48,879 --> 00:05:51,600
I only did it out of respect for you,

87
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:53,800
and did my best to indulge him.

88
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:56,199
Where is he?

89
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,399
I came here today

90
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,399
to take him to turn himself in.

91
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,319
What he committed

92
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:05,079
is a serious crime.

93
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,279
Could you really do that?

94
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,439
Even if he committed the gravest crime,

95
00:06:09,519 --> 00:06:11,480
I'll face the consequences with him.

96
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,399
Good.

97
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:14,480
You really are a good father.

98
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,360
Then let me give you a hand.

99
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:45,079
Scream!

100
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,000
Your voice

101
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:53,120
is the most beautiful melody in the world.

102
00:06:58,079 --> 00:06:59,959
I'm completely intoxicated by it.

103
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:03,800
Crying?

104
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:06,120
What good is crying?

105
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:09,120
Crying only shows weakness.

106
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,759
And too much crying ruins your looks.

107
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,839
Don't touch me!

108
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,639
That's more like it.

109
00:07:30,279 --> 00:07:31,279
Anger.

110
00:07:32,279 --> 00:07:33,720
Anger is what I want.

111
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:37,199
An angry woman fuels my desire to conquer.

112
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:44,079
Why have you become like this?

113
00:07:44,439 --> 00:07:46,439
Why have you become like this?

114
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:51,199
You don't need to understand.

115
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:54,040
You just need to obey.

116
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,639
Ruolan.

117
00:07:57,519 --> 00:07:59,519
If you hadn't tried to outsmart me,

118
00:08:03,079 --> 00:08:06,120
I'd have treated you well for a lifetime.

119
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:09,800
Forget it, forget it.

120
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,879
Acting is tiring, and no one's paying me.

121
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:15,759
Scream!

122
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,000
Scream as loud as you can!

123
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:20,240
The louder you scream, the more I like it.

124
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:30,920
How about it, Chief Xing?

125
00:08:31,959 --> 00:08:33,279
Your son's tastes

126
00:08:33,639 --> 00:08:35,120
are quite unique, aren't they?

127
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:36,200
Still,

128
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,960
those Red Gloves really suit him.

129
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,320
I'll ask you one last time.

130
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:47,279
Where is he?

131
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:50,879
Somewhere

132
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:55,039
no one will ever find him.

133
00:09:03,679 --> 00:09:05,000
You're an accomplice too.

134
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,320
Even if you strangle me,

135
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:10,759
it won't wash away your son's crimes.

136
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:13,320
Where is he?

137
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,000
I don't believe

138
00:09:19,399 --> 00:09:20,720
a criminal investigation captain

139
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:23,440
would dare to kill.

140
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,720
I'm begging you.

141
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,600
Tell me,

142
00:09:42,799 --> 00:09:43,759
where is he?

143
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:48,840
No one else can get hurt.

144
00:09:52,919 --> 00:09:54,320
I give you my word.

145
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:57,480
If you help me keep Li Kaiyang in check,

146
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,399
Zhao Ruolan

147
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,480
will be safe.

148
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,799
You're just letting him walk away?

149
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:21,320
A Tai.

150
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,480
Boss.

151
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:27,080
You know what to do, right?

152
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:30,120
Understood.

153
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:39,840
Ruolan,

154
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:44,679
you are the only woman I've ever loved.

155
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:49,080
The only woman in this world I care about.

156
00:10:53,399 --> 00:10:56,080
Let's have an open and honest chat, okay?

157
00:10:59,039 --> 00:11:00,720
Let's play a little game now.

158
00:11:01,879 --> 00:11:03,000
You ask, I answer.

159
00:11:07,879 --> 00:11:09,600
You want to ask about Ma Shijiang, right?

160
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,759
You must hate him to death right now.

161
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:14,440
But let me tell you,

162
00:11:15,399 --> 00:11:16,399
you're hating the wrong man.

163
00:11:18,159 --> 00:11:19,639
An idiot like him,

164
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:23,600
how could he enjoy your perfect body?

165
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,320
Let me tell you,

166
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:29,279
let me reveal the truth to you right now.

167
00:11:30,399 --> 00:11:31,360
That day,

168
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:35,120
I followed him into that room.

169
00:11:59,039 --> 00:11:59,559
Who's there?

170
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:00,720
Who's out there?

171
00:13:45,639 --> 00:13:46,679
Brilliant, isn't it?

172
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,600
Just a little trick

173
00:13:50,759 --> 00:13:53,519
and Ma Shijiang became my scapegoat.

174
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:03,960
Demon.

175
00:14:05,279 --> 00:14:06,840
You're nothing but a demon.

176
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,440
A demon?

177
00:14:11,879 --> 00:14:13,039
I am a devil king

178
00:14:13,799 --> 00:14:17,960
who makes even demons tremble.

179
00:14:22,559 --> 00:14:24,960
If you'd obeyed me sooner,

180
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:27,240
Ma Shijiang wouldn't have had to die.

181
00:14:28,759 --> 00:14:30,720
Neither would your brother.

182
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:39,120
Ptui!

183
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,320
Keep spitting. Go on, keep spitting.

184
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,960
Keep it up, keep it up.

185
00:14:45,919 --> 00:14:47,039
Spit, spit.

186
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:49,720
Since you refuse to behave,

187
00:14:50,399 --> 00:14:51,960
I have no reason to be gentle anymore.

188
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:53,960
Let go!

189
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:00,519
Dad.

190
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,200
Are you sure you saw it clearly?

191
00:15:12,559 --> 00:15:13,240
Chief Xing.
